      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"1. OUR BEAVER has been close to a win, finishing in the minors three on end before a fourth when checked in the run last time in a Grade 6 at Angle Park (35.40). Given another chance. 5. LEGS ELEVEN has been in the minors the last two, the latest showing strong pace early but gathered in and finished a 1.3 lengths third over 595m Angle Park in 35.11. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Expected to be in the finish again. 8. ALGORITHM has been in the money at his last two runs, most recently when third beaten 6 lengths (31.04). Goes well here including a win and five minors. Must be included in calculations. 2. YARRAMUNDI COCO ran good time (38.25) when third last start over 643m at this track, the second placing in a row. Safe beginner who should be prominent to the first bend.\",\"runners\":[1,5,8,2],\"exclusive\":false}",
